The matter is continued for initial appearance on 01-10-22 at 1:30 p.m.  Bail is set at $5,000.00 recognizance bond with the conditions that he report to the Two Rivers Police Department for fingerprints, photographs and identifying information within 48 hours or, if incarcerated, within 72 hours of release and defendant is to have no contact with M.R.A., DOB: 04-14-1998 or any residence or premises that person occupies.
